Personal:
- took a shorter shower (5L saved)
- turned off water when brushing teeth or washing hands/face (1.5L saved)
- ran a full load in the dishwasher or washing machine (3L saved)
- fixed a dripping faucet (1000L saved)
- scraped dishes instead of rinsing before loading the dishwasher (9L saved)

